  "title": "[수험생보약 잘 짓는 한의원] 수험생의 집중력향상과 최상의 컨디션을 위한 총명공진단(총명환)",
  "addDate": "2014. 6. 10.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "parentCategoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220026392768",
  "html_size": 188977,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220026392768\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220026392768\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; background-color: rgb(246, 243, 145);'><strong>수험생보약엔 이수한의원 총명공진단/총명환</strong></span></p><p><span style='font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style='font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>명의 허준의 동의보감에는</span><span style='font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>\"</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>잊어버리기를 잘하는 것을 치료하여 장복하면 하루에 천 마디의 말을 외울 수 있다</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;\" 고 </span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>나와있습니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a7c7743f0e8ff57f.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"271\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);.53px; rheight: 271.53284671532844px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20140610_56/isuhani_1402387315185nIp2K_JPEG/Exam-Revision-Nightmare-Make-It-Easy-and-Follow-These-Tips_e.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A9850C0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a7c7743f0e8ff57f.jpg\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>수험생은 장시간 앉아서 공부를 하기 때문에 생기는 운동부족과 스트레스로 인해 소화불량, 두통, 기억력감퇴, 집중력저하가 중요한 시기에 문제가 될 수 있습니다.</span></p><p><span style='font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>수능당일까지 최상의 컨디션을 유지해야 하기 때문에&nbsp;</span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;\">수험생의 건강관리에서 가장 중요한 부분은 체력보강과 집중력향상</span></strong>입니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>비염, 아토피 등 만성질환이 있는 경우엔&nbsp;그에 알맞은 탕약을 주로 처방을 받지만, 다른 질병이 없고 체력보강과 집중력향상을 위해서는 총명공진단/총명환이 효과가 가장 뛰어납니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;'><strong><u>이수한의원에서는 체력과 집중력향상을 위한&nbsp;탕약과 환약을 처방하고 있습니다.</u></strong></span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p></span><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;'><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(178, 235, 134);\">-</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(178, 235, 134);\">&#8203;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(178, 235, 134);\"> 총명탕</span></strong></span></p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8124cae49023bfea.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"383\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(106, 101, 187);.75px; rheight: 383.75px; rwidth: 500px;\" id=\"20140610_7/isuhani_1402395011442pdG0E_JPEG/P6103057.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A9850C0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8124cae49023bfea.jpg\"></div><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>체질과 현재 몸 상태맞게 처방하고 1일&nbsp;2회 복용하게 됩니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(244, 213, 237);'><strong>- 총명공진단</strong></span></p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0093a2d9aa3b5890.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"384\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);.12px; rheight: 384.1240875912409px; rwidth: 500px;\" id=\"20140610_276/isuhani_1402399990641iOFxA_JPEG/P6103061.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A9850C0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0093a2d9aa3b5890.jpg\"></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>이수한의원의 총명공진단은 </span><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>1일 1회 아침에 복용하게 됩니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 167, 0);'><strong>- 총명환</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"left\"><iframe src=\"/storyphoto/Arrange.naver?type=layout&xmlPath=https://blogfiles.pstatic.net/20140610_149/isuhani_1402400171998NI7ms_XML/StoryPhoto.xml&downloadDomain=https://blogfiles.pstatic.net&width=550&height=413\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" frameborder=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" title=\"포스트에 첨부된 스토리포토\"></iframe></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>이수한의원의 총명환은 1일 2회 복용하게 됩니다. </span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif;'>단, 진료 후 몸상태에 따라 3회 복용하는 경우도 있습니다.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 16, 21); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</span><strong><font face=\"Malgun Gothic\"><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 16, 21); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">이수한의원 총명공진단/총명환의 효능</span></font></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;- 체력을 길러주며 면역력 증진</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;- 눈과 머리를 맑게 해주고 긴장감과 스트레스 해소</span></p><p><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'>&nbsp;- 집중력 향상과 기억력 증진</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style='color: rgb(149, 16, 21); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'><strong>요즘 학생들은 예전보다 키도 크고 팔다리고 길어진 반면 기초체력은 확실히 많이 떨어졌습니다.</strong></span></p><p><strong><span style='color: rgb(149, 16, 21); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'>이수한의원 총명공진단/총면환은 수험생 뿐 아니라&nbsp;학업을 병행하는 직장인,&nbsp;국가고시를 준비하는&nbsp;</span><span style='color: rgb(149, 16, 21); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;'>고시생 등 학업에 지친분들도 꾸준하게 복용하시면 더욱 좋습니다.</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><div align=\"right\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4f4237ae54db16b6.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"125\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);.6px; rheight: 125.60000000000001px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20140610_140/isuhani_1402401766503PldIa_PNG/C7D1C0F8C1F8B7E1BD%A9%A3A32.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000333A9850C0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4f4237ae54db16b6.png\"></div><div align=\"right\" style=\"text-align: right;\"></div><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style='color: rgb(149, 16, 21); font-family: \"나눔고딕코딩\",NanumGothicCoding,Sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;'><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 문의 02-584-1075</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
